            "content_html": "<p>阅读 GPT-4 技术报告后的一点感想，链接：<a href=\"https://ar5iv.labs.arxiv.org/html/2303.08774\">https://ar5iv.labs.arxiv.org/html/2303.08774</a></p>\n",
            "url": "https://amireon.github.io/posts/LLMs-GPT-4",
            "title": "GPT-4技术报告阅读笔记",
            "date_modified": "2024-06-04T00:00:00.000Z",
